Lumi Jelly PNGTuber character repository
Copyright 2026 Sunwood AI Labs

Lumi Jelly artwork was created with OpenAI's built-in Image Gen tool on
2026-07-15 and 2026-07-16. The production runtime images preserve the generated artwork;
local processing is limited to chroma-key removal, transparent padding, and
resizing.

This character package targets PuruPuru PNGTuber, originally developed by masa
and published at:
https://github.com/rotejin/PuruPuruPNGTuber

PuruPuru PNGTuber is not bundled in this repository. Its software is available
under Apache License 2.0, and its visual assets have separate terms defined by
the upstream project.

The verification screenshot includes the PuruPuru PNGTuber user interface.
Rights and terms for that interface remain with masa and the upstream project;
the screenshot is included as a non-commercial project-introduction and
verification image under the upstream asset terms.
